column9: This cheap, good value Pizzeria place serves good Greek style gyros. A nice change to the usual kebab fare, prices are similar so it is a perfect spot for those who like fast food but are tired of falafel/burgers/pizza/kebab.

column7: Very good pizza for a good price and great crust
